  "intent": "Run the second part of the NEBNext RNA prep kit to isolate RNA using magnetic beads. Basically add beads to your samples, do some heating steps on the thermocycler, then use the magnetic module to pull down the beads and wash them a bunch of times with different buffers. At the end you elute the clean RNA and move it to a fresh plate. The robot pauses a few times so you can move the plate to the thermocycler for the heating steps.",
